The '''black-lored cisticola''' ('''''Cisticola nigriloris''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Cisticolidae]]. It is found in [[Malawi]], [[Tanzania]], and [[Zambia]]. Its natural [[habitat]] is [[subtropical or tropical dry shrubland]].

